# ==============================================================================
# DOCKER CONTEXT ARCHITECTURAL MANIFEST: .dockerignore
# EVOLUTIONARY STAGE: ROUND 10 (CHAINED CONTEXT: deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-Coder)
# ARCHITECTURAL PATTERN: HYBRID EXCLUSION HIERARCHY WITH MULTIPLE SEGMENTATIONS
# ==============================================================================
# This manifest leverages a 10-layered exclusion hierarchy with multi-segment exclusion logic
# to minimize the build context entropy, preserving high-fidelity layer caching
# and cryptographic-grade isolation of sensitive development artifacts.

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# LAYER 1: VIRTUAL CONTROL SURFACE & VERSIONING METADATA
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Prevents the injection of VCS state into the ephemeral container runtime.
# - Exclude `.git/` and its subdirectories for repository metadata.
# - Exclude `.github/` for GitHub Actions and workflows.
# - Exclude `.gitignore` and `.gitattributes` for Git configuration files.
# - Exclude `.hg` for Mercurial version control.
# - Exclude `.svn` for Subversion version control.
# - Exclude `.bzr` for Bazaar version control.
# - Exclude `_darcs` for Darcs version control.
# - Exclude `.history/` for VCS history metadata.
# - Exclude `.idea/` for Intellij IDEA project settings.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.git
.git/*
.github/
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.gitmodules
.hg
.svn
.bzr
_darcs
.history/
.idea/

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# LAYER 2: DEVELOPMENT ENVIRONMENT SHADOWING (IDE/LOCAL)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# High-granularity exclusion of local developer configuration fragments.
# - Exclude `.vscode/` for Visual Studio Code project settings.
# - Exclude `.vscode-test/` for testing configurations.
# - Exclude `.project` for Eclipse project settings.
# - Exclude `.classpath` for Eclipse classpath settings.
# - Exclude `.settings/` for Eclipse workspace settings.
# - Exclude `factorypath` for Eclipse factory path settings.
# - Exclude `sublimeproject` for Sublime Text project settings.
# - Exclude `sublimeworkspace` for Sublime Text workspace settings.
# - Exclude `externalToolBuilders/` for external tool builders.
# - Exclude `Dockerfile.local` for local Dockerfile.
# - Exclude `Dockerfile.development` for development Dockerfile.
# - Exclude `docker-compose.local.yml` for local docker-compose file.
# - Exclude `.env.local` for local environment variables.
# - Exclude `.env.development.local` for local development environment variables.
# - Exclude `.env.test.local` for local testing environment variables.
# - Exclude `.env.production.local` for local production environment variables.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.vscode/
.vscode-test/
.project
.classpath
.settings/
(factory)path
(sublime)project
(sublime)workspace
.externalToolBuilders/
	Dockerfile.local
Dockerfile.development
docker-compose.local.yml
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# LAYER 3: MULTI-RUNTIME DEPENDENCY GRAPH ISOLATION
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Prevents host-specific binary contamination of the container filesystem.
# - Exclude `/node_modules/` for Node.js dependencies.
# - Exclude `/bower_components/` for Bower dependencies.
# - Exclude `/npm-debug.log*` for npm debug logs.
# - Exclude `/yarn-debug.log*` for yarn debug logs.
# - Exclude `/yarn-error.log*` for yarn error logs.
# - Exclude `/.pnpm-debug.log*` for pnpm debug logs.
# - Exclude `/npm/` for npm cache.
# - Exclude `/yarn/` for yarn cache.
# - Exclude `/pnpm-store/` for pnpm store.
# - Exclude `/npmrc` for npm config file.
# - Exclude `/yarnrc` for yarn config file.
# - Exclude `/yarnrc.yml` for yarn config file.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/node_modules/
**/bower_components/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.pnpm-debug.log*
.npm/
.yarn/
.pnpm-store/
.npmrc
.yarnrc
.yarnrc.yml

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# LAYER 4: ARCHITECTURAL FRAGMENT - Python / AI-ML Ecosystem (EXPANDED)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Siphoned Logic: deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-Coder often handles massive AI/ML datasets.
# - Exclude `/__pycache__/` for Python bytecode cache.
# - Exclude `/*.py[cod]` for Python source files.
# - Exclude `/*$py.class` for Python compiled classes.
# - Exclude `/.pytest_cache/` for pytest cache.
# - Exclude `/.mypy_cache/` for mypy cache.
# - Exclude `/.ruff_cache/` for ruff cache.
# - Exclude `/.tox/` for tox environment files.
# - Exclude `/.nox/` for nox environment files.
# - Exclude `/.ipynb_checkpoints/` for Jupyter notebooks.
# - Exclude `/venv/` for virtual environments.
# - Exclude `/env/` for virtual environments.
# - Exclude `/.venv/` for virtual environments.
# - Exclude `/.env/` for environment variables.
# - Exclude `/pip-log.txt` for pip logs.
# - Exclude `/pip-delete-this-directory.txt` for pip cache.
# - Exclude `/.aws/` for AWS credentials.
# - Exclude `/.aws-sam/` for AWS SAM environment files.
# - Exclude `/.aws-sam/local/` for AWS SAM environment files.
# - Exclude `/requirements.txt` for pip requirements.
# - Exclude `/pyproject.toml` for pip project configuration.
# - Exclude `/setup.py` for Python package setup.
# - Exclude `/README.md` for project documentation.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.tox/
**/.nox/
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/
**/venv/
**/env/
**/.venv/
**/.env/
**/pip-log.txt
**/pip-delete-this-directory.txt
**/.aws/
**/.aws-sam/
**/.aws-sam/local/
**/requirements.txt
**/pyproject.toml
**/setup.py
**/README.md

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# LAYER 5: PRESENTATION LAYER & COMPILED ARTIFACTS
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Prevents pre-built artifacts from polluting the deterministic build process.
# - Exclude `/dist/` for compiled artifacts.
# - Exclude `/lib/` for library artifacts.
# - Exclude `/out/` for output artifacts.
# - Exclude `/build/` for build artifacts.
# - Exclude `/bin/` for executable artifacts.
# - Exclude `/obj/` for object artifacts.
# - Exclude `/release/` for release artifacts.
# - Exclude `*.tsbuildinfo` for TypeScript build info.
# - Exclude `*.map` for compiled maps.
# - Exclude `*.d.ts` for TypeScript definitions.
# - Exclude `*.js.map` for JavaScript maps.
# - Exclude `*.dll.map` for DLL maps.
# - Exclude `*.so.map` for shared object maps.
# - Exclude `*.lib.map` for library maps.
# - Exclude `*.a.map` for archive maps.
# - Exclude `*.la.map` for linker maps.
# - Exclude `*.lo.map` for loader maps.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
/dist/
/lib/
/out/
/build/
/bin/
/obj/
/release/
*.tsbuildinfo
*.map
*.d.ts
*.js.map
*.dll.map
*.so.map
*.lib.map
*.a.map
*.la.map
*.lo.map

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# LAYER 6: AI MODEL WEIGHTS & LARGE DATASET FRAGMENTS (EXPANDED)
